Condition.name: A4_WF_1x_3x_Rule
Condition.description: Checks for Documents if the User is not in the External Role Checks for E Designs and Products if the User is not in the External Role or Part of Standadization Group Or if Part of the DBA Group

Condition.name: A4_WF_2x_Rule
Condition.expression: ((u.role_name!="TemporaryStaff") AND (u.role_name!="Creator") AND (Condition::A4_WF_Default_Rule(o, t, u)=true)) OR (u.fnd0ConditionHelper.fnd0isSubGroupOf(u.group, "dba") = true)
Condition.description: Checks for Altreps and Documents if the User is not in the External or TemporaryStaff Role Checks for E Designs and Products if the User is not in the External or TemporaryStaff Role or Part of Standadization Group Or if Part of the DBA Group

Condition.name: A4_WF_60_61_Rule
Condition.description: Checks for Documents if the User is not in the External Role Or if Part of the DBA Group

Condition.name: A4_WF_62_63_Rule
Condition.expression: ((o != null) AND (u.role_name!="External") AND ((u.fnd0ConditionHelper.fnd0isSubGroupOf(u.group, "Standardization") = false) AND ((o.object_type="A4_E_DesignRevision") OR (o.object_type="A4_ProductRevision")))) OR (u.fnd0ConditionHelper.fnd0isSubGroupOf(u.group, "dba") = true)
Condition.description: Checks for Altreps if the User is not in the External Role Checks for E Designs and Products if the User is not in the External Role or Part of Standadization Group Or if Part of the DBA Group

Condition.name: A4_WF_Default_Rule
Condition.expression: ((o != null) AND (u.role_name!="External") AND ((o.object_type="A4_DocumentRevision") OR (u.fnd0ConditionHelper.fnd0isSubGroupOf(u.group, "Standardization") = false) AND ((o.object_type="A4_E_DesignRevision") OR (o.object_type="A4_ProductRevision"))))
Condition.description: Checks for Documents if the User is not in the External Role Checks for E Designs and Products if the User is not in the External Role or Part of Standadization Group

Condition.name: A4_WF_General
Condition.expression: ((o != null) AND ((o.object_type="A4_E_DesignRevision") OR (o.object_type="A4_DocumentRevision") OR (o.object_type="A4_ProductRevision") OR (o.object_type="A4_Change_ItemRevision"))) OR (u.fnd0ConditionHelper.fnd0isSubGroupOf(u.group, "dba") = true)
Condition.description: Only checks the Object Type Allowed: E Design Altrep Product Document Change Item

Condition.name: A4_WF_Has_DSP_3D
Condition.expression: ( ((d.object_type="JPEG") AND (d.a4_doccategory="00_MBILD")) OR ((d.object_type="A4_STEP") AND (d.a4_doccategory="00_STP")) OR ((d.object_type="DirectModel") AND (d.a4_doccategory="00_JT")) OR ((d.object_type="HTML") AND (d.a4_doccategory="00_HTML")) )
Condition.description: Check for AI 3D Dispatcher translator results.

Condition.name: A4_WF_Has_DSP_ACADDWG
Condition.description: Check for ACADWDG Dispatcher translator results.

Condition.name: A4_WF_Has_DSP_AIDrawing
Condition.expression: ( ((d.object_type="PDF") AND (d.a4_doccategory="00_IDW")) OR ((d.object_type="PDF") AND (d.a4_doccategory="00_ZOM")) OR ((d.object_type="PDF") AND (d.a4_doccategory="00_EVT")) OR ((d.object_type="Zip") AND (d.a4_doccategory="00_DXF")) )
Condition.description: Check for AIDrawing Dispatcher translator results.
